column2: select top # id, s.bestobjID as objid, s.specObjID as specobjid, bptclass as bpt, lgm_tot_p5# as smass, sfr_tot_p5# as sfr, specsfr_tot_p5# as ssfr, d4#_n as d4#, lick_hb as hb, lick_hd_a as hd, lick_hg_a as hg from MyDB.temp as t left join SpecObjAll as s on s.bestObjID = t.objid left join galSpecExtra as x on s.specObjID = x.specObjID left join galSpecIndx as i on s.specObjID = i.specObjID order by id
